{"body": "Ideally there'd be a link to download the guides in .mobi format from the Rails website (I can't think of any reason why people should have to create them themselves - is there one?)\r\n\r\nI think the step-by-step is handy for those that will probably need it most - not everyone is familiar with Rails let alone command line.\r\n\r\nAnyway, not a problem, if you don't want to include it I'll post the step-by-step on my blog so at least it's out there (I'm sure it will come in handy for nubes like me).\r\n\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3390817", "created_at": "2012-01-06T21:08:44Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/4312#issuecomment-3390817", "updated_at": "2012-01-06T21:08:44Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 4312, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/AstonJ", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/dd460c62f8ce07dd7582925a3cc8d8aa?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fa3483d1b212c6fae683a3ddf1ca36817.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ/received_events", "gravatar_id": "dd460c62f8ce07dd7582925a3cc8d8aa", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "AstonJ", "type": "User", "id": 759626, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/AstonJ/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52382884bd3543c15100efb5"}, "id": 3390817, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/4312"}
